\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ saying, Make (sic) a treaty between me and you... And Ben Hadad heeded. And the kings of Aram 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ did not cease being adversaries to Israel until Ahaz died, and in the third year of Ahaz, the king of 
