\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ 200 years. How so? Amaziah reigned 29 years, Uzziah 52, Jotham 16, Ahaz 16, Hezekiah 29, 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Manasseh 55, Amon 2, totaling 200 less 1, in addition to those years that Joash lived after he had 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ repaired the Temple. We find that they would not have had to repair the damage of the Temple had 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ not the wicked Athaliah and her sons breached it. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ For Athaliah, etc.\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  It is therefore no wonder that it 
